{"tid":1273463,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要佔領！要佔領！要佔領！","createTime":"2019-07-01T14:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T15:18:24.000Z","uid":8092,"like":35,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"40c6f0c0ab1cde5c9b743959792ea34e27a5a798","tid":1273463,"uid":8092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:18:13.000Z","msg":"佔領一定係更好既選擇<br />\n<br />\n利申唔想任何人比人拉 前線想撤既話絕對支持 尤其如果有速龍入黎<br />\n<br />\n如果而家撤 現場既情況係好似成班示威者入去破壞完就走 咁樣真係會令聽日民意完全形容我地成為一堆暴民 純粹想搞破壞 但佔領既話可以長期令政府停擺 雖然各位義士會好危險 只有更多人入黎一齊佔領先會冇事！大家加油！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持長期佔領<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望義士撤退"},{"pid":"85e0ef06532a215fc8a88274871feb48f83f2773","tid":1273463,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"文宣幫傳<br />\n提防散水 <br />\n人少先危險<br />\n唔好信擇日再戰<br />\n全力支援現場決定<br />\n發夢香港人盡快出去支援準備反包圍<br />\n發夢需要各種補給<br />\n發夢需要照明燈<br />\n發夢三罷各路增緩<br />\n一定要頂住 堅持住！<br />\n香港要改變！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人要團結！<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n<br />\n一定要捉住今次機會<br />\n絕對唔好再浪費<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"88a37f30b959c1c3fa3c82e0a39a48718aa363b7","tid":1273463,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:19:12.000Z","msg":"需要人數"},{"pid":"dda9d98fa79b452d87b407f723527fa9b0c8d012","tid":1273463,"uid":8092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"Push 各位義士加油"},{"pid":"d7cd8ebeab108c91c011de8f29afc085d99f1345","tid":1273463,"uid":8092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3b82be4cce0f273fe2001a726b1d5bc564267be8","tid":1273463,"uid":8092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"各位義士戴番口罩please！"},{"pid":"c2e7e85efb269e96ace27b49c78cdbfa446f05a6","tid":1273463,"uid":8092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c